SUBENT        F0630003   20251216   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                  6         10
REACTION   (14-SI-28(A,INL)14-SI-28,PAR,DA/DA,G/A,AV)
ANG-SEC    (ANG,A)
           (ANG1,G)
DETECTOR   (SOLST) There were used thirteen particle detectors
           simultaneously over a range 115 to 170 degr. with
           respect to the incident beam axis.
SAMPLE     The target consisting of isotopically enriched 28Si2O
           had an areal density of 4.5*10**18 28Si nuclei per cm2.
STATUS     (CURVE,,R.Prasad+,J,NP/A,255,64,1975) Figs 6-8
